text: Richard Sutton (died 1634), of Lincoln's Inn and later of Acton, Middlesex, was an English politician and lawyer. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Newport, Isle of Wight in 1586 and for Newtown, Isle of Wight in 1589. ==References== Category:16th-century births Category:1634 deaths Category:Members of Lincoln's Inn Category:People from Acton, London Category:English MPs 1586–1587 Category:English MPs 1589
